<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_9.jpg" alt="表演后1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_10.jpg" alt="表演后2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_11.jpg" alt="表演后3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_12.jpg" alt="表演后4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_13.jpg" alt="表演后5"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_14.jpg" alt="表演后6"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_15.jpg" alt="表演后7"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180817_16.jpg" alt="晚上参加独奏音乐会"></p>
<p>8月18日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_3.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_4.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_5.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_6.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_7.jpg" alt="中国科技馆之旅5"></p>
<p>晚上我们参加了另外一场古筝名家的演奏会，我与我的几位偶像都合了影，太开心了！</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_8.jpg" alt="与姜淼老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_9.jpg" alt="与王冬婉老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_10.jpg" alt="与赵勃楠老师合影"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_11.jpg" alt="参加了另外一场古筝名家的演奏会"></p>
<p>8月19日：</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_1.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_2.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180819_3.jpg" alt="北京站乘车回家3"></p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201808/diary_20180818_2.jpg" alt="金奖证书"></p>
<p><iframe height="498" width="510" src="http://player.youku.com/embed/XMzc5MzI2OTM0MA==" frameborder="0" 'allowfullscreen'=""></iframe><br>我的展演古筝曲目“伊犁河畔”</p>
]]></content>
    
